rt automatic criteria are at worst $47.4\\%$ slower than the\noptimum and at best $16.5\\%$ slower.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 Apr 2021 20:32:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-06"}
