dm}$ package for the $\\texttt{R}$\nstatistical computing language; this package is available via CRAN, and the\nsource code is available on GitHub.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Apr 2021 13:29:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-06"}
